page.title: 14NETHERTON
page.content: NY0436 Across the A594 is a private housing estate built in the 1960's.It has bungalows,semi-detached houses.They are made of rendered brickwork with concrete tile roofs.There are gardens to the front and back of the houses but no amenities.The estate is being expanded to the north onto pasture land. ELLENBOROUGH ESTATE NY0436 This is a private housing estate behind ribbon development on the A594.It was built in the early 1970's and is composed of 132 semi-detached +12 detached houses and 29 bungalows.They are made of brickwork with concrete tiled roofs.They have gardens to the front and rear.Ther are no amenities but 2 large areas of deciduous woodland(approx 4 acres).
